<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Redefinicao de senha</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f6f1e8;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="24" border="0">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="max-width: 640px; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 14px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(22, 59, 52, 0.08);">
          <tr>
            <td>
              {{> header preheader="Recebemos um pedido para redefinir sua senha" appName=appName}}
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 26px 24px 12px 24px; font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; color: #212529;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 24px; line-height: 31px; color: #163b34;">Redefinir senha</h1>
              <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: #3c4643;">
                Oi{{#if name}}, {{name}}{{/if}}. Recebemos uma solicitacao para alterar sua senha.
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; line-height: 24px; color: #3c4643;">
                Clique no botao abaixo para criar uma nova senha.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 18px 24px 8px 24px;">
              <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #2a5654; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; line-height: 20px; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 10px;">
                Criar nova senha
              </a>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 8px 24px 24px 24px; font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; color: #5b6662; font-size: 13px; line-height: 20px;">
              {{#if expiresIn}}
              Este link expira em {{expiresIn}}.
              {{else}}
              Se voce nao solicitou essa alteracao, ignore este e-mail.
              {{/if}}
              <br />
              Se o botao nao funcionar, copie e cole este link no navegador:<br />
              <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="color: #2a5654;">{{resetUrl}}</a>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              {{> footer appName=appName supportEmail=supportEmail}}
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
